Home
[page]

<img src="/media/dp.jpg" class="right" alt="" />
<p>The D/P generation began in 2007 following the North American release of Pok&eacute;mon Diamond and Pearl. It introduced 107 new Pok&eacute;mon, the physical/special damage split, and Wi-Fi play. Currently, D/P is typically played online on the simulator <a href="http://pokemonshowdown.com/">Pokemon Showdown</a>. During the fourth generation (roughly 2007&ndash;2010), the most popular simulator was <a href="http://pokemonlab.com">Shoddy Battle</a>.</p>


